HEADWORD: glistening
<hw>glistening</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Reflecting light readily or in
large amounts; having a surface luster; reflecting light directly rather
than scattering it.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> glossy, nitid, sheeny, shiny.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

